             was indicted for <rs id="t17930410-85-off464" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17930410-85-off464" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17930410-85-off464" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17930410-85-cd465" type="crimeDate">11th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930410-85-off464 t17930410-85-cd465"></join>, twelve case knives, with ivory handles, value 1 l. 4 s. twelve forks, ditto, value 12 s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17930410-85-victim798" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Skidmore
