                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930410-85-defend796 t17930410-85-punish470"></join>
               Imprisoned six months in the house of Correction
            </rs>, and <rs id="t17930410-85-punish471" type="punishmentDescription">
