                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930410-85-defend796 t17930410-85-punish471"></join>
               fined 1 s
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice HEATH.</p>
